Dialogs.Dialog: Hey... If it's okay with you, how about you come to study at my house？ We have tests coming up, right？
Wanna come to study at my house？ You haven't studied for the coming tests, right？
Have you studied for the coming tests？ Wanna come to study at my house？
Then I'll see you after school.
Then come to my house after school.
Um, then let's meet at my house after school.
I see... Okay, do your best then.
Really？ Don't regret it later then...
I see. You want to study by yourself. Good student, huh？
Eh？ You're here... Right, if you have time, how about coming to my house to study for the tests？
Study for the tests？ Right, we have tests coming up...
Eh？ You're here... Ah, have you studied for the tests？ How about you come to study at my house？
Right, it's almost exam time again...
Eh？ I didn't expect to meet you here. Right, I got a nice idea. Let's study for the exams together. How's that？
Right, the exams are coming up...
Well... Then come to my house after this. I'll be waiting.
Then let's meet at my house later today. Don't be late, okay？
Then we'll meet after this. We have to study hard, okay？
I see. It's sudden, huh？ Sorry...
You turned me down... Well, it's probably so sudden. Sorry.
A-ha... You rejected me. What a pity. Maybe next time then.
I don't quite understand. How about we study together？
That's fine. Although I'm not confident that I can teach you, you can come to study at my house.
I don't quite understand. How about we study together？
Hehe, come to study at my house. I'll teach you then.
I don't quite understand. How about we study together？
Then come to study at my house. This is like I'm your tutor, huh？
It's your first time here, right？ This is a little embarrassing...
Yes... Well, I'll have to bother you today...
This is your first time to be here, right？ Don't do anything mischievous, okay？
Hehe. It's the first time that you're here. I feel a little nervous.
Welcome to my home. Now, let's get inside.
Okay, I have to bother you today.
Don't keep staring at things in my room like you did last time, okay？
I won't... Then I have to bother you today.
Okay, welcome to my home. I've always been waiting for you to come here. Hehe.
You're exaggerating again... Then I have to bother you today.
It's just a normal room, right？ There's nothing particularly interesting, so don't stare.
The only thing you can do in here is to sit down and stay still, okay？
Hehe... Are you nervous？ You can make yourself more comfortable.
You really can't calm down, can you...？ Hehe.
Let's sit there. That way you can't look around my room. It's embarrassing...
Are you still nervous？ Actually, I'm not used to something like this either.
Shall we sit over there？ Let's get started.
Hey, hey. Hurry up and take a seat....Where shall we start？
Now, shall we start our lesson reviews？
Shall we start？ Are you ready？
There will be a set of 3 questions. If you answer them all correctly, I'll give you a reward... Do you feel motivated now？
Ah, pass？ Okay, I got it.
It wasn't a difficult one, though. Hehe...
It can't be helped. So, we'll skip this one.
Ah, amazing. You got them all correct. I'll give you a reward.
You got them all correct. You really can do it. Then I'll have to give you a reward, right...？
You got them all. Hehe... Then my reward for this is...
Hehe. Your reward this time is this...
Wait a second. I'll be right back.
Too bad... It's regrettable, but you missed one question...
You made one wrong answer. I can't give you a reward.
You missed one question. I can't give you a reward, okay？
Hmm, you want to quit, huh...？
Hehe... If it's like this, I'll have to tutor you very hard, huh？
Don't mind, don't mind. Don't lose your heart with just something like this.
Yes, the most important thing is not to give up.
You still haven't learned anything much, right？
It can't be helped. Well, I'll try to cheer you up a little bit.
...It'd be better if you come a little closer.
Hehe... Hey, you know what to do, right？
Hey, just a little bit... Okay？
This is what you gave me. How is it？ Does it suit me？
Do you remember this outfit？ Now, may I ask your opinion about it？
Okay, as a reward, I'm wearing the outfit you gave me. How is it？
Occasionally, I wear something like this... How is it？
Hey, how is it？ I look different, right？
I ended up wearing this. Hehehe... Are you happy？
It's enough, right？ This is really embarrassing, you know？
Okay, enough for the service. Hehe. Looking at me like that won't help.
Okay, this is it. If I keep this on for too long, it won't be called a special anymore.
How about this？ If you get more questions correct, I'll wear something else. Hehe.
Okay, I knew this would be your answer.
Hey, this is very special, okay？
Hey, I've done this much for you. If you still don't feel motivated, I have nothing to say.
Hey... Don't look at me like that.
It's a special service for you, okay？
How long are you going to keep looking？
It's about time we should stop this.
...You aren't looking at places where you shouldn't look, right？
No, where are you looking at？
What？ Don't stare at places where you shouldn't look, okay？
You don't have to stare so enthusiastically like that.
Maybe it's because of this outfit that my heart is pounding so hard...
Wearing this outfit is just too embarrassing...
Then this is it for today.
Hehe, you really tried your best.
We've studied a lot today, right？
You did your best. I'll give you a "good job" stamp.
You'll have to try a little harder, okay？
I'm quite worried about the coming exams...
Things didn't go well today but I guess we can manage it somehow, right？
Geez. You made me worried. You must study after you get home, all right？
Then do your best for the tests. I'll do my best, too. Hehe.
I think we have covered everything for the tests. ...You wanna go home now？
Can I stay for a while？
Then wait a moment. I have something to show you.
We have spent our time productively.
I don't know why things turned out to be like that... But if there's a chance, let's do this again.
In the middle of our study, we did some strange things...
